Package me.Salt.Command.Commands.Informative

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GuildInfoCommand
    This command returns information to the command executor with information about the current guild that the command was executed in.
    HelpCommand
    This command provides useful help information about the bot, commands, utilities and useful links.
    InfoCommand
    This command returns information about a specified User, TextChannel, VoiceChannel, Guild, or the bot itself.
    PingCommand
    This command calculates a ping value (in milliseconds) and returns the value to the command executor.
    ProfileInfoCommand
    This command provides information to the command executor about a specified user's profile.
    RatesCommand
    This command provides details to the user about Discord's rate limits applicable to bots.
    StatisticsCommand
    This command calculates, formats and provides detailed statistics on the bot, such as current Uptime and the total thread count.
    TextChannelInfoCommand
    This command provides information to the command's executor about the current TextChannel.
    UptimeCommand
    This command provides simplistic information about the bot's current uptime.
